_sText:
These five maps were created in order to help teams to train in attack and defense of one bomb site per map. I tried to keep the visual mood of maps to give up the feeling of playing in the real maps.
I hope these maps will be useful for teams wishing to gain experience and strategies on these 5 maps :

- de_dust2_only_b : Restricted access to the site B.
- de_inferno_only_a : Restricted access to the site A.
- de_nuke_only_int : Restricted access to the inside of the factory.
- de_train_only_b : Restricted access to the site B.
- de_tuscan_only_a : Restricted access to the site A.
